_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 569, \"end\": 574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999994232613816, \"rank\": 5.767389410752514e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nabil Boudi said, \\\"The boxer Imane Khelif has decided to begin a new fight, a fight for justice, dignity and honour,\\\" reportedAFP.He further noted, \\\"The investigation will determine who was behind this misogynist, racist and sexist campaign, but will also have to concern itself with those who fed the online lynching.\\\"\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 909, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 619, \"end\": 631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421623295, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 25-year-old became a victim of online harassment after her first fight against Italian boxer Angela Carini.\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 1022, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 994, \"end\": 1001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9941558593022028, \"rank\": 0.004485061785717588, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1008, \"end\": 1021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103662667, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bout concluded within 46 seconds 